DESCRIPTION

ci-better-lang is supposed to be a CodeIgniter language library extending the original CI Language class
giving the developer opportunity to create much more flexible translation phrases.


USAGE

code: $this->lang->phrase('Welcome');
return: Welcome

code: $this->lang->phrase('Welcome to %website%, %name%', array('%website%'=>'www.github.com', '%name%'=>'Blagomir Ivanov'));
return: Welcome to www.github.com, Blagomir Ivanov
